{"type":"answer","id":227350,"parentType":"question","parentId":22595,"uid":7997,"contents":"大家都知道饮用水也分高低贵贱，正如“张华喝着395欧元一瓶的Fillico；李萍用着60刀海淘的限量VOSS瓶子发自拍；我在百货公司卖农夫山泉：我们都有光明的前途”<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9Nh24iU.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9Nh24iU.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9Nh24iU.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center><i>价值395欧的FILLICO® \"Destiny Love II\"™</i></center><br>\n近来百货公司进了一批新货，那么下面就由我来介绍一下这个你们从没有荷过的船新版本——来自极致北境冰岛的<i>Kranavatn® </i>(<s>读作Coronavirus<i>™</i></s>)<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ES6jsVV.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ES6jsVV.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ES6jsVV.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center><i>A premium water brand from Iceland</i></center><br>\n完美瓶身由钛合金纯手工打造，premium彰显与众不同<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/o9nr6zN.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o9nr6zN.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/o9nr6zN.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n水源地分别取自天然瀑布<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xqfhPdv.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xqfhPdv.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xqfhPdv.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n和千年蓝冰融水<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/YS1yv9x.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YS1yv9x.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/YS1yv9x.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/i9CB0hq.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i9CB0hq.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/i9CB0hq.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n按照1:1:1黄金比例配方秘制而成！<br>\n而Kranavatn<i>®</i>的秘制法宝，就在于它的过滤工序极端坚持纯天然、原生态，不使用任何人造机器！<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kFrQYT7.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kFrQYT7.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kFrQYT7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/mww3Hy5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mww3Hy5.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mww3Hy5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center><i>\"Kranavatn®纯净水，通过熔岩进行数百年的自然过滤\"</i></center><br>\n然而Kranavatn®最值得称道的是它的销售渠道<br>\n此项目由冰岛政府背书，并在首都修建了6个总计容积2400万升专用于储存Kranavatn®的水箱<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/R96VCHB.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/R96VCHB.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/R96VCHB.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center><i>位于雷克雅未克的6个水箱</i></center><br>\n只要购置一台Kranavatn®私人提取终端，您就可以终生免费享用Kranavatn®<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gTYROeA.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gTYROeA.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gTYROeA.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gCAj3Di.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gCAj3Di.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gCAj3Di.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center><i>Kranavatn®私人提取终端</i></center><br>\n哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈相信看到这你也民白了<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/bgwOwO9.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bgwOwO9.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/bgwOwO9.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/J2Itt9B.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J2Itt9B.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/J2Itt9B.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\nKranavatn其实就是冰岛自来水😏<br>\n虽然目前主要发达国家均可安全直饮自来水，但大多口感确实不敢恭维。而笨探长有幸喝过的冰岛自来水，口感极佳，入口是清爽的微甜，刷牙洗脸都是一种享受。所以冰岛人没有去超市买矿泉水的习惯，都是直接拧开自来水，咕咚咕咚喝下肚。据说当地人安慰失恋友人都是这样：你渴了吗？我倒一杯自来水给你喝<br>\n<br>\n不可否认，如今国外很多发达地区的瓶装水销售份额屡创新高，越来越多的影视作品也让剧中角色在家喝矿泉水而非自来水，毕竟“符合饮用水最低安全标准”的自来水在观感上已经输给代表着现代工业文明和消费文化的瓶装水了。以至于一些喝了一辈子自来水的安大略老哥甚至产生了自我怀疑——“<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/AskAnAmerican/comments/7hdlco/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">难道只有我一直在喝自来水吗？</a>”<br>\n<br>\n当然，百货公司卖农夫山泉的笨探长在出门吃饭回应服务员充满消费暗示的\"Can I get you something to drink\"时......<br>\n<br>\n\"Tap water, please.\" 三个词，深藏功与名<br>\n<br>\n以上😉","date":"2020-04-03","agreeCount":23,"discussionCount":1}